{"tid":1377423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到好撚心痛","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:52:02.000Z","uid":137540,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91f48c51348e6070c24588c275e396fd09fba8d3","tid":1377423,"uid":137540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"拉咗好多義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開槍開到麻木晒 好似大家都慣會開槍咁<br />\n班狗癲撚咗狂開 槍聲不斷<br />\n點解我覺得前線勇武好似做緊人肉盾咁<br />\n唔主動衝 淨係守住 越嚟越多人落單<br />\n永遠尊重前線 但真係唔想再見到咁多人送頭<br />\n加上尋日先去完元朗 大家都可能好攰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一邊睇一邊喊<br />\n和理非真係要幫下手<br />\n去機場同罷工都要有"},{"pid":"eeab9effc4fdca28d04c59e8c27c3aec7b403eda","tid":1377423,"uid":4602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}